2026-05-14T05:35:19.8088505Z 223        <!--
2026-05-14T05:35:19.8089108Z 224            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-14T05:35:19.8089995Z 225            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-14T05:35:19.8091129Z 226            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-14T05:35:19.8091957Z 227            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-14T05:35:19.8092674Z 228            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
